If you want, I can generate three variants in the same symbolic-rendering grammar:
	1.	sunrise / foggy atmosphere (lighter palette)
	2.	storm / dramatic chiaroscuro (heavier o/#)
	3.	“mosaic” style (tile blocks instead of points)